{"tid":2131864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"許智峯擬提私人草案修改大學法例 禁特首任校監必然制","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T03:13:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"faf30fd2200a5b3c98b89bd8c3107399486a399a","tid":2131864,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/5NLESIHQCBEL3QEHE2U5GTCURU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2F5NLESIHQCBEL3QEHE2U5GTCURU%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=5a8a92d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2F5NLESIHQCBEL3QEHE2U5GTCURU%2F&h=7a1b19a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/5NLESIHQCBEL3QEHE2U5GTCURU/</a><br />\n<br />\n港大校委會早前通過解僱法律系副教授戴耀廷。雖然戴日前表明將就結果向校監即特首林鄭月娥，惟他坦言上訴不可能成功。民主黨立法會議員許智峯草擬私人條例草案，修訂教資會轄下大學法例之規定，如特首任校監必然制等，以保障大學自主。他希望能在年底新立法會會期提出。"},{"pid":"3e404ed26cd49fa47fbd2609c0a1b0b81de53276","tid":2131864,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0f149c7b4141dcf64f169a61569ab49053780c","tid":2131864,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"智勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0302dc3d6368c8422eb31d35a5b20ba0b37ff7","tid":2131864,"